{"data":[{"type":"question_feed_card","target_type":"answer","target":{"admin_closed_comment":false,"annotation_action":null,"answer_type":"normal","attached_info":"ogEPCAQQAxjK3eiCAiC26+IKkgIkCgkxMjg3NTYwOTESCTU0Mjc4MTEzMBgEIgpJTUFHRV9URVhU","author":{"avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-459402a1c96f4012865064c7488de458_l.jpg?source=1def8aca","avatar_url_template":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-459402a1c96f4012865064c7488de458.jpg?source=1def8aca","badge":[],"badge_v2":{"detail_badges":[],"icon":"","merged_badges":[],"night_icon":"","title":""},"exposed_medal":{"avatar_url":"","description":"","medal_id":"0","medal_name":""},"follower_count":65,"gender":-1,"headline":"想尝尝黄酒的味道","id":"5a57b894e88f26ca7ad7013c594454b8","is_advertiser":false,"is_followed":false,"is_following":false,"is_org":false,"is_privacy":false,"name":"鲸鱼的京","type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5a57b894e88f26ca7ad7013c594454b8","url_token":"jing-yu-de-jing-33","user_type":"people"},"can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"collapse_reason":"","collapsed_by":"nobody","comment_count":83,"comment_permission":"all","content":"\u003cp data-pid=\"wjcefms4\"\u003e统一回复：不会带任何人，也不会回答任何问题，这世界上哪有免费的东西嘛！况且我也懒得挣你的钱，很累的…现在带着几个朋友已经愁的头疼…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"TI6TStUH\"\u003e做游戏工作室的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"-n6Eb_ys\"\u003e去年身无分文，找姥姥借了三千块钱，买了两台破电脑，干起了工作室…然后赚了钱继续买，就这么莫名其妙干到现在…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"HK5WpCxc\"\u003e以前住在别人家的浴室里，穷到没钱和女孩子约会，爹妈也从来没帮过忙，倒是每个月会分别给他俩几千块钱…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"Mg3p9Nbd\"\u003e现在也没挣到一百万吧…但一年七八十万还是有的…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"YLgLUX0O\"\u003e有时候看到知乎上很多问题问什么怎样月入一万，怎样副业月入几千…怎样年收入达到多少多少，其实有些困惑…很难吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"waTCX62l\"\u003e这不是我在装逼，只是我几乎没有过正式的工作，也几乎没有过稳定的生活。当然，也没有奢求过太多，所以穷也好富也好都一个样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"9J1Fc2uM\"\u003e虽然比不上大多数牛逼哄哄的人，但好歹能生活富足，衣食无忧，而且其实做到这一步几乎没有丝毫难度，就是玩这个游戏很多年了，熟悉套路，就一路走下来了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"focw7peJ\"\u003e嗯…对，问的是如何白手起家挣一百万对吧…我的回答是：好好玩游戏…\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca class=\"video-box\" href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/1052141148923076608\" target=\"_blank\" data-video-id=\"\" data-video-playable=\"\" data-name=\"\" data-poster=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c5d6c78ab9ef3086f872b66fe7d27c61.jpg\" data-lens-id=\"1052141148923076608\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c5d6c78ab9ef3086f872b66fe7d27c61.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cspan class=\"content\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"title\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"z-ico-extern-gray\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"z-ico-extern-blue\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"url\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"z-ico-video\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003ehttps://www.zhihu.com/video/1052141148923076608\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","content_mark":{},"content_need_truncated":false,"created_time":1543630077,"decorative_labels":[],"editable_content":"","excerpt":"统一回复：不会带任何人，也不会回答任何问题，这世界上哪有免费的东西嘛！况且我也懒得挣你的钱，很累的…现在带着几个朋友已经愁的头疼… 做游戏工作室的。 去年身无分文，找姥姥借了三千块钱，买了两台破电脑，干起了工作室…然后赚了钱继续买，就这么莫名其妙干到现在… 以前住在别人家的浴室里，穷到没钱和女孩子约会，爹妈也从来没帮过忙，倒是每个月会分别给他俩几千块钱… 现在也没挣到一百万吧…但一年七八十万还是有的…","extras":"","favlists_count":173,"force_login_when_click_read_more":false,"id":"542781130","is_collapsed":false,"is_copyable":true,"is_jump_native":false,"is_mine":false,"is_navigator":false,"is_normal":true,"is_sticky":false,"is_visible":true,"matrix_tips":"108 赞同 · 173 收藏 · 83 评论","navigator_vote":false,"question":{"created":1390522771,"id":"22590902","question_type":"normal","relationship":null,"title":"如何白手起家挣到一百万？","type":"question","updated_time":1514280825,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/22590902"},"reaction_instruction":{},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"upvoted_followees":[],"voting":0},"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_text":"","relevant_type":""},"reshipment_